Revision history for Perl extension Lingua::JA::Mail.

0.03  2005-09-23 09:00:00 JST
	- Added preconvert function for some symbol characters.

0.02  2003-04-03 02:45:23 JST
	- The manner about handling for UTF-8 has changed.
	- Users encouraged to `use utf8;' pragma in their source code.

0.01  2003-04-01 05:14:15 JST
	- rivesed to Lingua::JA::Mail & Lingua::JA::Mail::Header
	  from their ancestor Mail::ISO2022JP
	- rather improved methods and interface.

0.00  2003-03-05~2003-03-31
	- original version as Mail::ISO2022JP v0.01~0.05
